{"tid":1626174,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"nba球隊火箭GM出Tweet撐香港抗爭 余文樂：你媽死了","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:21:39.000Z","uid":68738,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"5f18122414c7bc220b738028e528dfe40935a349","tid":1626174,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/vw8XHGFnrY5t3RiGI1wsCywah_E=/720x405/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/Z7JFLIOZH3AAOU5MA6V7QXJ6VE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fvw8XHGFnrY5t3RiGI1wsCywah_E%3D%2F720x405%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZ7JFLIOZH3AAOU5MA6V7QXJ6VE.jpg&h=c16308ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港府宣佈訂立《蒙面法》引發全民怒火，身在東京的火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）今早亦在Twitter上載有FightForFreedom及StandWithHongKong字句的標誌，支持香港的民主運動，不過該帖隨即惹來中國網民不滿，香港明星余文樂亦留言辱罵莫利。<br />\n<br />\n莫利發出帖文後，獲得不少香港網民讚好，並留言感激其支持，但同時亦惹來大批持反對意見的網民圍攻，當中余文樂亦以英語留言「What do u mean（你是甚麼意思）」。<br />\n<br />\n眼見群情洶湧，莫利在1小時後已刪去有關帖文，並換上了張東京日出的相片，留言「Tokyo wakes up」，希望平息風波，但一眾網民仍舊咄咄逼人，繼續進行罵戰，余文樂亦再度加入戰團，留言指罵莫利「Your mom is died（你的母親死了）」。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者曾就事件向余文樂求證，但暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191005/JQVC3SBGZU5VZZVWLROMWZOJS4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191005%2FJQVC3SBGZU5VZZVWLROMWZOJS4%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=70560664\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191005%2FJQVC3SBGZU5VZZVWLROMWZOJS4%2F&h=85507431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191005/JQVC3SBGZU5VZZVWLROMWZOJS4/</a>"},{"pid":"0a86c1eaffc73e7ec6ee18c038e95f9ae96bcbcb","tid":1626174,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-